{"title":"诗传单","authors":["张志民","草禹"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":9,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗传单"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毒菌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张志民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个肮脏的灵魂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最喜欢阴暗的地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用毒汁作胭脂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用细菌作衣裳……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时也穿件漂亮的裙子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想冒充是一种“花”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但它实在不是花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为它见不得太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右派分子回到家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草禹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右派分子回到家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似大雪天里吞凉茶："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妻子默默地走进厨房"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女儿气鼓鼓地嘟着嘴巴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小儿子只顾洗着红领巾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大儿子瞪起眼睛看着他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有那只哈巴狗儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向他懒洋洋地摇了摇尾巴。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}